title: Kendall Jenner and a boob-flashing Bella Hadid lead the way at supermodel dinner date in London
text:

Kendall Jenner and her supermodel pals like Bella Hadid and Hailey Baldwin spend most of the year jetting around the world for work. 
So when they’re all in the same city it’s inevitable that they'll come together for a big catch up, which is just what happened when Kendall and co descended on London ahead of London Fashion Week. 
But, being a group of young, glamorous and successful supermodels, it was no ordinary dinner date. 
The group chose to meet up at exclusive restaurant Sexy Fish before heading to Box night club, and certainly stood out from the crowd in their eye-catching outfits. Kendall's outfit had a rock chick vibe (Photo: WENN.com) Bella flashed her boobs in a barely there top (Photo: WENN.com) The girls were snapped at Sexy Fish restaurant (Photo: FameFlynet) Kendall kept a baseball hat on all night (Photo: WENN.com) 
Keeping Up With The Kardashians star Kendall, 21, wore skin tight leather leggings, a music tee shirt and an oversized red fluffy coat, teamed with stiletto boots and a baseball cap. 
Bella, 20, meanwhile, went one further, flashing her boobs in a barely there mesh top, teamed with grungy black jeans covered in patches. She opted for biker boots, a long black coat and beret hat to finish her look. 
Also present was Taylor Hill, 20, who followed in Bella’s footsteps by letting it all hang out in a lacy bra covered by a sheer black top. They went clubbing after their meal (Photo: FameFlynet) Stella and Taylor were also at the gathering (Photo: WENN.com) Hailey teamed jogging bottoms with heels (Photo: WENN.com) 
Elsewhere, Stella Maxwell 26, chose to flash her toned abs in a black crop top. 
The final member of the group was Hailey Baldwin, 20, who looked positively demure in comparison, wearing an off the shoulder white shirt and grey tracksuit bottoms. 
LFW kicked off on Thursday and continues until Tuesday.
